<!--

USAGE example
<contentUrlSpecification contentType="Update" url="">
      <keyParam name="Update" type="CONTENT"/>
      <classParam name="com.manulife.pension.ps.web.taglib.search.UpdateURLContext" type="CLASS"/>
   </contentUrlSpecification>
   
if the classParam element is present then the url attribute is ignored, therefore, it can be set
to "". If the classParam element is not present then the application behaves as normal.
-->

